Class AbstractClassHierarchyNodeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.reef.tang.util.walk.AbstractClassHierarchyNodeVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NodeVisitor<Node>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GraphvizConfigVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractClassHierarchyNodeVisitor
extends Object
implements NodeVisitor<Node>
    Generic interface to traverse nodes of the class hierarchy. Dispatches between ClassNode, PackageNode, and NamedParameterNode types. It is used e.g. in Walk.preorder()
